Technologies Used

1. Salesforce Platform – Core CRM platform for project and task management.


2. Apex – Server-side programming for custom business logic and automation.


3. Lightning Web Components (LWC) – Modern UI for dynamic, responsive dashboards and components.


4. Salesforce Flow & Process Builder – Declarative automation for workflows, approvals, and notifications.


5. Salesforce Reports & Dashboards – Track project KPIs, tasks, and team performance.


6. REST API / Salesforce Connect – Integration with external tools like Jira, Trello, or databases.


7. Data Loader & Salesforce CLI (SFDX) – Bulk data management and deployment.


